<div class="prose dark:prose-invert mb-4 sm:mb-8 mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-center"><span class="text-4xl tracking-tight">Publish your writing effortlessly from your inbox</span></h1>
  <p>
    Publish your writing to a beautiful, minimalist website using your existing email account.
  </p>
  <p>
    Pagecord is great for long-form writing, but also for micro-blogging your thoughts.
    Compose your writing in your email editor and click send. Pagecord does the rest.
  </p>
  <p>
    Take a sneaky peek at <a href="https://pagecord.com/pagecord">the Pagecord blog</a> to see an example,
    or watch the video below to see it in action.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 text-center not-prose">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-semibold p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-bmc-pink">Create your free Pagecord today!</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <video class="w-full max-h-[500px] dark:border dark:border-slate-800 bg-black" controls poster="https://d1q3gzkzfltpo9.cloudfront.net/pagecord-intro-cover.jpg">
    <source src="https://d1q3gzkzfltpo9.cloudfront.net/pagecord-intro-2.mp4"
            type="video/mp4">
    Sorry, your browser does not support the video tag 😭
  </video>


  <h2 class="text-center">Fun features. Unbeatable Value 😇</h2>
  <p>
    Pagecord is super-simple to use, but it's chock-a-block with great features.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Bold, underline, lists or code</strong>. All your favourite email formatting is supported 🖋️</li>
    <li><strong>Long-form writing or microblog</strong>. Write long-form articles with rich text, or microblog your thoughts. Both look fantastic 🎨</li>
    <li><strong>Media Embeds</strong>. Links to YouTube, Spotify and Bandcamp are automatically embedded. Great for sharing your favourite tunes and videos 🎧 📺</li>
    <li><strong>Follow your friends</strong>. Follow other Pagecord sites and see the latest articles in your personal feed 🤝</li>
    <li><strong>RSS feeds</strong>. Every site has a public RSS feed. You get a private RSS feed of all your followee's posts too! 📑</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Premium customers get a lot more features for an unbeatable price of only <strong>$<%= Subscription.price %> per year</strong>!
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Image Attachments</strong>. Attach images to your email and they'll auto-magically appear in your posts 🪄</li>
    <li><strong>Custom Domains</strong>. If you'd prefer to use you own domain name for your site, set it up in one click 🌐</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-center">Open source 🤓</h2>
  <p>
    The Pagecord code is <a href="https://github.com/lylo/pagecord">open source under the MIT license</a>. Take a look under the hood,
    suggest improvements, or (if you're feeling brave) host it yourself!
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 text-center not-prose">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-semibold p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-bmc-pink">Create your free Pagecord today!</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h3 class="text-center tracking-tight">Subscribe to Pagecord updates</h3>
  <%= render "newsletter_form" %>

</div>
